  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. confirm as Pompe disease

          2. Age 4 and can speak 2-words sentence by order

          3. mild to severe hypernasality

          4. have regular speech therapy for 8 weeks or longer

        Exclusion Criteria:

        (1）hearing loss （2）congenital pharyngeal or laryngeal structure anomalies including cleft
        palate （3）cerebral palsy （4）recent otitis media effusion （5）very severe hypernasality
        （6）use non-invasive ventilator
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
